HEADWORD: Ingesta
<hw>In*ges"ta</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n. pl.</pos> <ety>[NL. See
<er>Ingest</er>.]</ety> <fld>(Physiol.)</fld> <def>That which is
introduced into the body by the stomach or alimentary canal; -- opposed
to <contr>egesta</contr>.</def>⟦br⟧
